  "customHelp": "Green = Harvester (gather energy). Red = Reaper (hunt). When you PLAY a Reaper or Harvester it enters your HOME zone. A creature can't push into TO INVADE (the opponent's area) until your NEXT turn (no invading the turn it's played). COUNTERS in order: Energy | Balance. ENERGY = your spendable pool this turn (Raw + Life merged into one to cut clicks) — gain it at Dawn, spend it, convert leftover to Population at Dusk. BALANCE = your score. POPULATION = red pips placed on your Harvesters (this is what accumulates). Treachery = drag the Treachery token (target pip) from the token tray onto the 1-10 track above To Invade (start it on 5). Play 1 Creator from your Creator Deck pile at start of turn. Tokens: target pip = Treachery, red pip = Population, black = Death.",
